e_size\":51.34700000000000130739863379858434200286865234375},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f9d059e\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<h2 class=\\\"intertitre\\\" style=\\\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1em !important; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-weight: 400; color: #111111; line-height: 1.1; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\">Tournoi de tennis f\\u00e9minin WTA !<\\/span><\\/h2><p style=\\\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\"><strong style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\\\">Rendez-vous sur les courts du\\u00a0<a style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; color: #000000; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-weight: bold;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.jds.fr\\/strasbourg\\/tennis\\/tennis-club-de-strasbourg-5782_L\\\">Tennis Club de Strasbourg<\\/a>\\u00a0du 18 au 26 mai 2018<\\/strong>\\u00a0pour conna\\u00eetre la prochaine gagnante des Internationaux de Strasbourg apr\\u00e8s Sam Stosur (2017), Caroline Garcia (2016), Samantha Stosur (2015), Monica Puig (2014), Aliz\\u00e9 Cornet (2013) Francesca Schiavone (2012), Andr\\u00e9a Petkovic en 2011 et Maria Sharapova en 2010.<\\/span><\\/p><h2 class=\\\"intertitre\\\" style=\\\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1em !important; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-weight: 400; color: #111111; line-height: 1.1; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\">Un \\u00e9v\\u00e8nement sportif tr\\u00e8s attendu<\\/span><\\/h2><p style=\\\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\">Ce tournoi majeur du tennis fran\\u00e7ais a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 cr\\u00e9\\u00e9 en 1987. Derni\\u00e8re ligne droite avant les Internationaux de France \\u00e0 Roland Garros, les Internationaux de\\u00a0<a style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; color: #000000; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-weight: bold;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.jds.fr\\/strasbourg-390_V\\\">Strasbourg<\\/a>\\u00a0permettent aux joueuses de jouer dans des conditions similaires \\u00e0 celle du Tournoi du Grand Chelem \\u00e0 Paris.<\\/span><\\/p><h2 class=\\\"intertitre\\\" style=\\\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1em !important; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-weight: 400; color: #111111; line-height: 1.1; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\">Des stars du tennis f\\u00e9minin \\u00e0 Strasbourg<\\/span><\\/h2><p style=\\\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\">De nombreuses joueuses internationales ont foul\\u00e9 la terre battue des terrains strasbourgeois au cours des derni\\u00e8res \\u00e9ditions des Internationaux de Strasbourg. On peut citer : Marion Bartoli, Am\\u00e9lie Mauresmo, Steffi Graf ou encore Maria Sharapova.<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #000000;\\\">En 2017, quelques grandes joueuses \\u00e9taient pr\\u00e9sentent sur les courts strasbourgeois : Roberta Vinci (Italie - 35e mondiale, 10 titres WTA), Caroline Wozniacki (Danemark - 11e mondiale, 25 titres WTA). La fran\\u00e7aise\\u00a0<strong style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\\\">Caroline Garcia<\\/strong>\\u00a0(25e mondiale), vainqueur des IS 2016, viendra remettre son titre en jeu !<\\/span><\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"baaab9f\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":33,\"_inline_size\":24.21900000000000119371179607696831226348876953125},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"051422b\",\"elType\":\"widget