"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"345074f\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 10px; color: #000000; font-family: proximanova-regular, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #e56ea9;\\\">Le 14 avril 2018<\\/span><\\/div><div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 10px; color: #000000; font-family: proximanova-regular, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\\\"><p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #e56ea9;\\\">Auditorium des Mus\\u00e9es\\u00a0<\\/span><br style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\\" \\/><span style=\\\"color: #e56ea9;\\\">1 place Hans Jean Arp - 67000 Strasbourg<\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: #000000; font-family: proximanova-regular, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #e56ea9;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-family: proximanova-bold, sans-serif;\\\">de Carl Theodor Dreyer<\\/strong><\\/span><br style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\\" \\/><span style=\\\"color: #e56ea9;\\\">Muet, romance et drame\\u00a0\\u00a0 \\u00a0 1 h 29 min\\u00a0<\\/span><br style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\\" \\/><br style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\\" \\/><span style=\\\"color: #e56ea9;\\\">Avec Walter Slezak, Max Auzinger, Nora Gregor<\\/span><\\/p><h3 style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: proximanova-bold, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #a56a79; margin: 0px; font-size: 10px; text-transform: none; padding-top: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #e56ea9;\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-family: proximanova-bold, sans-serif;\\\">Soir\\u00e9e pr\\u00e9sent\\u00e9e par Georges Heck<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h3><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: #000000; font-family: proximanova-regular, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\\\"><br style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\\" \\/><span style=\\\"color: #e56ea9;\\\">\\u00ab Maintenant, je peux mourir en paix, car j\'ai vu le grand amour. \\u00bb Apr\\u00e8s avoir prononc\\u00e9 ces mots, le grand peintre Claude Zoret rend son dernier souffle. Un amour vou\\u00e9 \\u00e0 son \\u00e9l\\u00e8ve Micha\\u00ebl, mais que ce dernier ne lui rend pas.<\\/span><\\/p><h2 style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: proximanova-regular, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #a56a79; margin: 0px; font-size: 10px; text-transform: none; padding-top: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #e56ea9;\\\">Synopsis<\\/span><\\/h2><p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: #000000; font-family: proximanova-regular, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #e56ea9;\\\">Dans la vaste demeure du peintre Claude Zoret, Micha\\u00ebl, son mod\\u00e8le pr\\u00e9f\\u00e9r\\u00e9 devenu son fils adoptif, montre \\u00e0 d\'\\u00e9l\\u00e9gants invit\\u00e9s un de ses tableaux. La princesse Zamikoff vient demander au ma\\u00eetre de faire son portrait. Elle devient, par la suite, la s\\u00e9ductrice du jeune Micha\\u00ebl. Le journaliste Switt tente d\'instruire Claude Zoret de l\'attitude de son prot\\u00e9g\\u00e9. Or, celui-ci, revenu au foyer, use de flatteries trompeuses pour emprunter au peintre de fortes sommes d\'argent\\u00a0; plus tard, il lui volera m\\u00eame une de ses \\u0153uvres les plus remarquables. Zoret finit par lui pardonner et en fait son l\\u00e9gataire universel. Gravement malade, Claude Zoret s\'\\u00e9teint dans une profonde solitude, le c\\u0153ur certes d\\u00e9\\u00e7u mais encore plein d\'indulgence.<\\/span><\\/p><\\/div>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"76fed0f\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":25,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"ea129a9\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/127.0.0.1:8888\\/Strasbourg\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/04\\/info_5-min.png\",\"id\":99},\"image_size\":\"sydney