lass=\\\"intertitre\\\" style=\\\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1em !important; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-weight: 400; color: #111111; line-height: 1.1; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #4054b2;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #e56ea9;\\\">Un \\u00e9v\\u00e8nement sportif tr\\u00e8s attendu<\\/span><\\/h2>\\n<p style=\\\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #4054b2;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #e56ea9;\\\">Ce tournoi majeur du tennis fran\\u00e7ais a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 cr\\u00e9\\u00e9 en 1987. Derni\\u00e8re ligne droite avant les Internationaux de France \\u00e0 Roland Garros, les Internationaux de\\u00a0<a style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; color: #e56ea9; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-weight: bold;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.jds.fr\\/strasbourg-390_V\\\">Strasbourg<\\/a>\\u00a0permettent aux joueuses de jouer dans des conditions similaires \\u00e0 celle du Tournoi du Grand Chelem \\u00e0 Paris.<\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<h2 class=\\\"intertitre\\\" style=\\\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1em !important; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-weight: 400; color: #111111; line-height: 1.1; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-spac