(101, 1, '2018-04-14 23:10:40', '2018-04-14 21:10:40', '<h3></h3><h3 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1.5em !important; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-weight: 400; color: #111111; line-height: 1.1; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-decoration: underline;\">Internationaux de Strasbourg 2018</h3><h2 style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1em !important; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-weight: 400; color: #111111; line-height: 1.1; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Tournoi de tennis féminin WTA !</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\">Rendez-vous sur les courts du <a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; color: #000000; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.jds.fr/strasbourg/tennis/tennis-club-de-strasbourg-5782_L\">Tennis Club de Strasbourg</a> du 18 au 26 mai 2018</strong> pour connaître la prochaine gagnante des Internationaux de Strasbourg après Sam Stosur (2017), Caroline Garcia (2016), Samantha Stosur (2015), Monica Puig (2014), Alizé Cornet (2013) Francesca Schiavone (2012), Andréa Petkovic en 2011 et Maria Sharapova en 2010.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1em !important; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-weight: 400; color: #111111; line-height: 1.1; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Un évènement sportif très attendu</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Ce tournoi majeur du tennis français a été créé en 1987. Dernière ligne droite avant les Internationaux de France à Roland Garros, les Internationaux de <a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; color: #000000; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.jds.fr/strasbourg-390_V\">Strasbourg</a> permettent aux joueuses de jouer dans des conditions similaires à celle du Tournoi du Grand Chelem à Paris.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1em !important; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-weight: 400; color: #111111; line-height: 1.1; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Des stars du tennis féminin à Strasbourg</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">De nombreuses joueuses internationales ont foulé la terre battue des terrains strasbourgeois au cours des dernières éditions des Internationaux de Strasbourg. On peut citer : Marion Bartoli, Amélie Mauresmo, Steffi Graf ou encore Maria Sharapova.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">En 2017, quelques grandes joueuses étaient présentent sur les courts strasbourgeois : Roberta Vinci (Italie - 35e mondiale, 10 titres WTA), Caroline Wozniacki (Danemark - 11e mondiale, 25 titres WTA). La française <strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\">Caroline Garcia</strong> (25e mondiale), vainqueur des IS 2016, viendra remettre son titre en jeu !</p>		\n										<img width=\"230\" height=\"405\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_1-min-230x405.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_1-min-230x405.png 230w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_1-min-170x300.png 170w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_1-min-350x617.png 350w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_1-min-480x846.png 480w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_1-min.png 506w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 230px) 100vw, 230px\" />											\n		<h3 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1.5em !important; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-weight: 400; color: #111111; line-height: 1.1; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-decoration: underline;\">NL Contest Strasbourg 2018</h3>\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1.5em !important; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-weight: 400; color: #111111; line-height: 1.1; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-decoration: underline;\">L\'évènement glisse de Strasbourg</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Chaque année, l\'association Nouvelle Ligne propose un grand concours de roller, skate, BMX, trottinette, monocycle mais aussi de l’escalade, un tournoi de streetball, un battle de breakdance, du slackline, des démos de parkour, des concerts, du Graffiti, des DJ, des événements offs, des soirées, un village exposants et de nombreuses animations.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Une Grande Scène musicale, qui se tiendra sur deux jours avec le Foreign Beggars et Don Choa x Dj Djel (Fonky Family).</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Programme du NL Contest 2018</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\">Vendredi 18 mai 2018</strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />12h : Ouverture des portes <br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />13h-14h : Qualification Freestyle Scooter Amateur Street<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />14h30-16h30 : Qualification BMX Street Amateur<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />14h30-16h30 : SlideBox Flat Contest<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />15-16h30 : Qualification + Finale Spine Freestyle Scooter<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />17h-19h : Qualification Roller Street Amateur + Roller Street Girl<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />18h-19h : Battle Of The Beat<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />19h-21h : Concerts Foreign Beggars + Salad\' Tomat\' Onion<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />23h-04h : Vicius Party @ Fat <br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" /><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\">Samedi 19 mai 2018</strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />10h : Ouverture des portes<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />11h -12h : Qualification BMX Street Amateur (suite)<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />12h-18h30 : Breaking NL Contest<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />12h-14h : Qualification BMX DIRT<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />12h30 - 13h30 : Qualification Roller Street Amateur (suite)<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />14h -14h30 : Finale Freestyle Scooter Amateur Street<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />14h-16h : Qualification + Finale Spine BMX<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />14h30-15h15 : Qualification + Finale Roller Halfpipe<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />15h15-16h30 : Qualification Roller Street PRO<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />17h-19h : Qualification + Finale Spine Roller<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />17h15-18h15 : Qualification BMX Street PRO<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />18h : Finale Breaking NL Contest<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />18h45-19h30 : Finale BMX Street Amateur<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />19h-21h : Concerts Don Choa x DJ Djel + Strasbourg All Stars<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />19h30-20h30 : Qualification Skate Halfpipe <br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />23h-05h : Clubbing ZOO BASS x NL Contest @ La Laiterie<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" /><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\">Dimanche 20 mai 2018</strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />11h : Ouverture des Portes<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />11h-19h : Streetball NL Contest<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />12h30-13h30 : Finale Roller Street Amateur<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />13h-14h30 : Qualification + Finale Spine Skate<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />13h45-14h00 : Finale Roller Girl Street<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />14h30-15h30 : Qualification+ Finale Freestyle Scooter Street PRO<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />15h30 -16h15 : Finale Skate halfpipe<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />15h30 -16h30: Finale BMX Dirt<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />16h15 -17h15 : Finale Roller Street PRO<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />17h45 - 18h45 : Finale BMX street PRO<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />18h30-19h : Finale Streetball NL Contest<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />22h - 04h : Soirée de clôture Dinguerie Vol4 @ Mudd Club</p>		\n										<img width=\"230\" height=\"152\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_2-min-230x152.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_2-min-230x152.png 230w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_2-min-300x199.png 300w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_2-min-768x509.png 768w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_2-min-1024x678.png 1024w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_2-min-830x550.png 830w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_2-min-350x232.png 350w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_2-min-480x318.png 480w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_2-min.png 1268w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 230px) 100vw, 230px\" />											\n		<h1 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1.5em !important; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-weight: 400; color: #111111; line-height: 1.1; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-decoration: underline;\">Run and Dance</h1><p>La fête continue avec la 4ème édition de la course la plus colorée de l’année ! Un parcours de 5 km de course à pied avec 4 colors zones, un show DJ de 2h à l’arrivée et beaucoup d’autres surprises…<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" />2 000 dossards disponibles.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15.6px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" />Une discothèque éphémère sur la ligne d’arrivée.</p>		\n										<img width=\"230\" height=\"151\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_3-min-230x151.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_3-min-230x151.png 230w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_3-min-300x196.png 300w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_3-min-768x503.png 768w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_3-min-1024x671.png 1024w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_3-min-830x544.png 830w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_3-min-350x229.png 350w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_3-min-480x314.png 480w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_3-min.png 1240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 230px) 100vw, 230px\" />											\n		<h1 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1.5em !important; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-weight: 400; color: #111111; line-height: 1.1; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-decoration: underline;\">Course d\'obstacles Break Race à Strasbourg 2018</h1><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\">La course d\'obstacles de Strasbourg est de retour le dimanche 26 août 2018 !</strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />La 3ème édition de la Break Race de Strasbourg, c\'est un défi de 10 km et de plus de 20 obstacles à relever seul ou en équipe ! Attention, la course est limitée à 1 600 coureurs (âge minimum 16 ans).<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />Au programme : du fun, de l’eau, de la boue, des sourires, de la bonne humeur mais surtout de la gloire !<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" /><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-weight: bold; color: #000000;\" href=\"https://www.le-sportif.com/CalendarDetail/CalendarDetail.aspx?EventID=143032\">Inscriptions en ligne</a></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Pack inscriptions :<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />Le dossard<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />Le T-shirt Break Race<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />La médaille Break Race à l\'arrivée<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />2 Ravitaillements pendant la course, 1 ravitaillement et une bière à l\'arrivée</p>		\n										<img width=\"230\" height=\"332\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_4-min-230x332.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_4-min-230x332.png 230w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_4-min-208x300.png 208w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_4-min-350x506.png 350w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_4-min-480x694.png 480w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_4-min.png 584w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 230px) 100vw, 230px\" />											\n		<h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1.5em; margin: 10px 0px 0px; font-family: proximanova-bold, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #2d2d2d; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0px 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">MIKAËL</h1>Le 14 avril 2018<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Auditorium des Musées <br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />1 place Hans Jean Arp - 67000 Strasbourg</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"> </p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: #000000; font-family: proximanova-regular, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-family: proximanova-bold, sans-serif;\">de Carl Theodor Dreyer</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Muet, romance et drame     1 h 29 min <br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Avec Walter Slezak, Max Auzinger, Nora Gregor</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: proximanova-bold, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #a56a79; margin: 0px; font-size: 10px; text-transform: none; padding-top: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-family: proximanova-bold, sans-serif;\">Soirée présentée par Georges Heck</strong></h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: #000000; font-family: proximanova-regular, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />« Maintenant, je peux mourir en paix, car j\'ai vu le grand amour. » Après avoir prononcé ces mots, le grand peintre Claude Zoret rend son dernier souffle. Un amour voué à son élève Michaël, mais que ce dernier ne lui rend pas.</p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: proximanova-regular, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #a56a79; margin: 0px; font-size: 10px; text-transform: none; padding-top: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Synopsis</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: #000000; font-family: proximanova-regular, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Dans la vaste demeure du peintre Claude Zoret, Michaël, son modèle préféré devenu son fils adoptif, montre à d\'élégants invités un de ses tableaux. La princesse Zamikoff vient demander au maître de faire son portrait. Elle devient, par la suite, la séductrice du jeune Michaël. Le journaliste Switt tente d\'instruire Claude Zoret de l\'attitude de son protégé. Or, celui-ci, revenu au foyer, use de flatteries trompeuses pour emprunter au peintre de fortes sommes d\'argent ; plus tard, il lui volera même une de ses œuvres les plus remarquables. Zoret finit par lui pardonner et en fait son légataire universel. Gravement malade, Claude Zoret s\'éteint dans une profonde solitude, le cœur certes déçu mais encore plein d\'indulgence.</p>		\n										<img width=\"230\" height=\"353\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_5-min-230x353.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_5-min-230x353.png 230w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_5-min-195x300.png 195w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_5-min-768x1179.png 768w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_5-min-667x1024.png 667w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_5-min-350x537.png 350w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_5-min-480x737.png 480w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_5-min.png 796w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 230px) 100vw, 230px\" />											\n		<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1.5em; margin: 10px 0px 0px; font-family: proximanova-bold, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #2d2d2d; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0px 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration: underline;\">LES DESSINS ORIGINAUX D’ARCHITECTURE DE LA CATHÉDRALE</h2>Du 11 février au 24 juin 2018Musée de l\'Œuvre Notre-Dame 3 place du Château - 67000 StrasbourgPrésentation de la salle de conservation des dessins de la cathédrale 		\n										<img width=\"230\" height=\"101\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_6-min-230x101.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_6-min-230x101.png 230w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_6-min-300x132.png 300w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_6-min-768x337.png 768w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_6-min-1024x449.png 1024w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_6-min-830x364.png 830w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_6-min-350x153.png 350w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_6-min-480x210.png 480w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_6-min.png 1364w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 230px) 100vw, 230px\" />', 'Plus d\'infos', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '31-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-04-14 23:10:40', '2018-04-14 21:10:40', '', 31, 'http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/2018/04/14/31-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
