(102, 1, '2018-04-14 23:16:54', '2018-04-14 21:16:54', '<h3></h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1.5em !important; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-weight: 400; color: #111111; line-height: 1.1; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-decoration: underline;\">Internationaux de Strasbourg 2018</h3>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1em !important; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-weight: 400; color: #111111; line-height: 1.1; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Tournoi de tennis féminin WTA !</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\">Rendez-vous sur les courts du <a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; color: #000000; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.jds.fr/strasbourg/tennis/tennis-club-de-strasbourg-5782_L\">Tennis Club de Strasbourg</a> du 18 au 26 mai 2018</strong> pour connaître la prochaine gagnante des Internationaux de Strasbourg après Sam Stosur (2017), Caroline Garcia (2016), Samantha Stosur (2015), Monica Puig (2014), Alizé Cornet (2013) Francesca Schiavone (2012), Andréa Petkovic en 2011 et Maria Sharapova en 2010.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1em !important; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-weight: 400; color: #111111; line-height: 1.1; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Un évènement sportif très attendu</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Ce tournoi majeur du tennis français a été créé en 1987. Dernière ligne droite avant les Internationaux de France à Roland Garros, les Internationaux de <a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; color: #000000; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.jds.fr/strasbourg-390_V\">Strasbourg</a> permettent aux joueuses de jouer dans des conditions similaires à celle du Tournoi du Grand Chelem à Paris.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 30px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1em !important; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-weight: 400; color: #111111; line-height: 1.1; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Des stars du tennis féminin à Strasbourg</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">De nombreuses joueuses internationales ont foulé la terre battue des terrains strasbourgeois au cours des dernières éditions des Internationaux de Strasbourg. On peut citer : Marion Bartoli, Amélie Mauresmo, Steffi Graf ou encore Maria Sharapova.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">En 2017, quelques grandes joueuses étaient présentent sur les courts strasbourgeois : Roberta Vinci (Italie - 35e mondiale, 10 titres WTA), Caroline Wozniacki (Danemark - 11e mondiale, 25 titres WTA). La française <strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\">Caroline Garcia</strong> (25e mondiale), vainqueur des IS 2016, viendra remettre son titre en jeu !</p>\r\n<img src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_1-min-230x405.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 230px) 100vw, 230px\" srcset=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_1-min-230x405.png 230w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_1-min-170x300.png 170w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_1-min-350x617.png 350w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_1-min-480x846.png 480w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_1-min.png 506w\" alt=\"\" width=\"230\" height=\"405\" />\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1.5em !important; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-weight: 400; color: #111111; line-height: 1.1; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-decoration: underline;\">NL Contest Strasbourg 2018</h3>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1.5em !important; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-weight: 400; color: #111111; line-height: 1.1; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-decoration: underline;\">L\'évènement glisse de Strasbourg</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Chaque année, l\'association Nouvelle Ligne propose un grand concours de roller, skate, BMX, trottinette, monocycle mais aussi de l’escalade, un tournoi de streetball, un battle de breakdance, du slackline, des démos de parkour, des concerts, du Graffiti, des DJ, des événements offs, des soirées, un village exposants et de nombreuses animations.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Une Grande Scène musicale, qui se tiendra sur deux jours avec le Foreign Beggars et Don Choa x Dj Djel (Fonky Family).</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Programme du NL Contest 2018</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; bo