g: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />18h30-19h : Finale Streetball NL Contest<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />22h - 04h : Soirée de clôture Dinguerie Vol4 @ Mudd Club</p>		\n										<img width=\"230\" height=\"152\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_2-min-230x152.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_2-min-230x152.png 230w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_2-min-300x199.png 300w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_2-min-768x509.png 768w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_2-min-1024x678.png 1024w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_2-min-830x550.png 830w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_2-min-350x232.png 350w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_2-min-480x318.png 480w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_2-min.png 1268w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 230px) 100vw, 230px\" />											\n		<h1 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1.5em !important; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-weight: 400; color: #111111; line-height: 1.1; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-decoration: underline;\">Run and Dance</h1><p>La fête continue avec la 4ème édition de la course la plus colorée de l’année ! Un parcours de 5 km de course à pied avec 4 colors zones, un show DJ de 2h à l’arrivée et beaucoup d’autres surprises…<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\" />2 000 dossards disponibles.<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15.6px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\" />Une discothèque éphémère sur la ligne d’arrivée.</p>		\n										<img width=\"230\" height=\"151\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_3-min-230x151.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_3-min-230x151.png 230w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_3-min-300x196.png 300w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_3-min-768x503.png 768w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_3-min-1024x671.png 1024w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_3-min-830x544.png 830w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_3-min-350x229.png 350w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_3-min-480x314.png 480w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_3-min.png 1240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 230px) 100vw, 230px\" />											\n		<h1 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1.5em !important; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-weight: 400; color: #111111; line-height: 1.1; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-decoration: underline;\">Course d\'obstacles Break Race à Strasbourg 2018</h1><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\">La course d\'obstacles de Strasbourg est de retour le dimanche 26 août 2018 !</strong><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />La 3ème édition de la Break Race de Strasbourg, c\'est un défi de 10 km et de plus de 20 obstacles à relever seul ou en équipe ! Attention, la course est limitée à 1 600 coureurs (âge minimum 16 ans).<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />Au programme : du fun, de l’eau, de la boue, des sourires, de la bonne humeur mais surtout de la gloire !<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" /><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: none; background: transparent none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-weight: bold; color: #e56ea9;\" href=\"https://www.le-sportif.com/CalendarDetail/CalendarDetail.aspx?EventID=143032\">Inscriptions en ligne</a></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Pack inscriptions :<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />Le dossard<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />Le T-shirt Break Race<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />La médaille Break Race à l\'arrivée<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\" />2 Ravitaillements pendant la course, 1 ravitaillement et une bière à l\'arrivée</p>		\n										<img width=\"230\" height=\"332\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_4-min-230x332.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_4-min-230x332.png 230w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_4-min-208x300.png 208w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_4-min-350x506.png 350w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_4-min-480x694.png 480w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_4-min.png 584w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 230px) 100vw, 230px\" />											\n		<h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1.5em; margin: 10px 0px 0px; font-family: proximanova-bold, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #2d2d2d; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0px 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">MIKAËL</h1>Le 14 avril 2018<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Auditorium des Musées <br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />1 place Hans Jean Arp - 67000 Strasbourg</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: #000000; font-family: proximanova-regular, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-family: proximanova-bold, sans-serif;\">de Carl Theodor Dreyer</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Muet, romance et drame     1 h 29 min <br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Avec Walter Slezak, Max Auzinger, Nora Gregor</p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: proximanova-bold, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #a56a79; margin: 0px; font-size: 10px; text-transform: none; padding-top: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; font-family: proximanova-bold, sans-serif;\">Soirée présentée par Georges Heck</strong></h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: #000000; font-family: proximanova-regular, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />« Maintenant, je peux mourir en paix, car j\'ai vu le grand amour. » Après avoir prononcé ces mots, le grand peintre Claude Zoret rend son dernier souffle. Un amour voué à son élève Michaël, mais que ce dernier ne lui rend pas.</p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: proximanova-regular, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #a56a79; margin: 0px; font-size: 10px; text-transform: none; padding-top: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Synopsis</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; line-height: 20px; color: #000000; font-family: proximanova-regular, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">Dans la vaste demeure du peintre Claude Zoret, Michaël, son modèle préféré devenu son fils adoptif, montre à d\'élégants invités un de ses tableaux. La princesse Zamikoff vient demander au maître de faire son portrait. Elle devient, par la suite, la séductrice du jeune Michaël. Le journaliste Switt tente d\'instruire Claude Zoret de l\'attitude de son protégé. Or, celui-ci, revenu au foyer, use de flatteries trompeuses pour emprunter au peintre de fortes sommes d\'argent ; plus tard, il lui volera même une de ses œuvres les plus remarquables. Zoret finit par lui pardonner et en fait son légataire universel. Gravement malade, Claude Zoret s\'éteint dans une profonde solitude, le cœur certes déçu mais encore plein d\'indulgence.</p>		\n										<img width=\"230\" height=\"353\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_5-min-230x353.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_5-min-230x353.png 230w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_5-min-195x300.png 195w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_5-min-768x1179.png 768w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_5-min-667x1024.png 667w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_5-min-350x537.png 350w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_5-min-480x737.png 480w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_5-min.png 796w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 230px) 100vw, 230px\" />											\n		<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1.5em; margin: 10px 0px 0px; font-family: proximanova-bold, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #2d2d2d; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0px 20px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration: underline;\">LES DESSINS ORIGINAUX D’ARCHITECTURE DE LA CATHÉDRALE</h2>Du 11 février au 24 juin 2018<p>Musée de l\'Œuvre Notre-Dame 3 place du Château - 67000 StrasbourgPrésentation de la salle de conservation des dessins de la cathédrale</p> 		\n										<img width=\"230\" height=\"101\" src=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_6-min-230x101.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_6-min-230x101.png 230w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_6-min-300x132.png 300w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_6-min-768x337.png 768w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_6-min-1024x449.png 1024w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_6-min-830x364.png 830w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_6-min-350x153.png 350w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_6-min-480x210.png 480w, http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/info_6-min.png 1364w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 230px) 100vw, 230px\" />', 'Plus d\'infos', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '31-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-04-15 16:21:03', '2018-04-15 14:21:03', '', 31, 'http://127.0.0.1:8888/Strasbourg/2018/04/15/31-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
